{"tid":876214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入一入黎，講你知點解咁多上深圳飲喜茶唱k打邊爐","createTime":"2018-10-25T12:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T18:34:37.000Z","uid":143306,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59d0c022f6ba95237519d7e51ba0711548eebca2","tid":876214,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為深圳的確係平靚正lo</span></span><br />\nLonely Planet 2019全球十大最佳旅遊城市：深圳第二 哥本哈根居首<br />\n<br />\nLonely Planet公布2019年全球十大最佳旅遊城市，丹麥首都哥本哈根（左圖）居首，深圳（右圖）排第二位。（VisitCopenhagen Instagram圖片/新華社/明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n著名旅遊指南Lonely Planet公布2019年全球十大最佳旅遊城市，丹麥首都哥本哈根居首，深圳、塞爾維亞城市諾維薩德分別排第二、第三位，大家計劃明年出走之旅時可參考一下！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2019年全球10大最佳旅遊城市</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 哥本哈根 Copenhagen（丹麥）<br />\n<br />\n2. 深圳 Shenzhen（中國）<br />\n<br />\n3. 諾維薩德 Novi Sad（塞爾維亞）<br />\n<br />\n4. 邁阿密 Miami（美國）<br />\n<br />\n5. 加德滿都 Kathmandu（尼泊爾）<br />\n<br />\n6. 墨西哥城 Mexico City（墨西哥）<br />\n<br />\n7. 達喀爾 Dakar（塞內加爾）<br />\n<br />\n8. 西雅圖 Seattle（美國）<br />\n<br />\n9. 薩達 Zadar（克羅地亞）<br />\n<br />\n10. 梅克內斯 Meknes（摩洛哥）<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Lonely Planet<br />\n<br />\n文：黃廷希 thwong02@mingpao.com<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1540283746154&amp;issue=20181023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1540283746154%26issue%3D20181023&d=M2bG9fiv1H7O7mhUogrt4f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ee30fb2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1540283746154%26issue%3D20181023&h=fe44983f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1540283746154&amp;issue=20181023</a>"},{"pid":"51faf871f07f1e2e2f5f45c82ce2330376291d9a","tid":876214,"uid":143306,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"冇人反對？"},{"pid":"6e11a746afaa5cfebf